window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Dominic, 26 years old and an MIT graduate, is an avid outdoorsman who likes to hunt. On one of his trips, he gets caught up in a storm and wakes up in another reality.</b></p> <p>It's a reality that has magic and fantastical creatures. Trying to cope with his new life, Dominic is given skills to help him blend into society. The main thing he has to remember is that females run this world.</p> <p><i>The Traveler </i>features unconventional relationships, sexual content, and cursing. It is intended for mature listeners.</p>"; 
